        Parameters:
        itemType - The line item's type. One of sku (for a product), tax (for taxes),or shipping (for shipping costs).
        itemDescription - The human-readable description for the line item.
        totalAmount - The total price of this line item.Note: This is the total price after multiplying by the quantity,not the price of an individual item.
        quantity - The quantity to display for this line item.
